      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING LIPA (1) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (30.39) last time in a OPEN at Rockhampton. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and four minor placings from 10 starts. Tough to beat if on-song. SUPER SPECIAL (3) continues to race in super honest form hitting the frame at four of nine career runs, winning two back before finishing third last time (35.25) over 600m at this track. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. ETERNITY BRIDGE (4) jumped from this same draw and was close to the lead throughout before boxing on well and holding a 3 length third (30.26) at this track over 520m in a Restricted WIN. Worth another try. HARA'S MILLY (7) boasts a solid strike-rate over this trip.",
